column5: Lawyer jokes are the best!!! Here's one for yah! Fishing related! What's the difference between a lawyer and a carp? One's a scum sucking bottom feeder and the other is a fish! There you go! I'm here all day! Roast beef is in the lobby! HH
What's the difference between a lawyer and a leech? After you die, a leech stops sucking your blood.   Rump-pa-da-pum!!
